problem_data.title: Maximum Length of Repeated Subarray
problem_data.description: Given two integer arrays nums1 and nums2, return the maximum length of a subarray that appears in both arrays.

examples.explanation: The repeated subarray with maximum length is [3,2,1].
The repeated subarray with maximum length is [0,0,0,0,0].
